# Review Pipeline Flow — Walkthrough

## Dispatch Logic

Khi user chọn mode **Renew**, system đọc style JSON:
- `"pipeline": "review"` → gọi [_do_renew_review()](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/ui/rewrite_style_tab.py#1815-2214) (**flow mới**)
- Không có hoặc khác → gọi [_do_renew_style()](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/ui/rewrite_style_tab.py#1374-1812) (**flow cũ, không sửa**)

